casebody.data:
Antonio M. NEAL, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4519 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed for lack of jurisdiction because the notice of appeal was filed more than 30 days after rendition of the order disposing of the motion for rehearing and is, therefore, untimely.

CASANUEVA, LUCAS, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
